{"tid":1589650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【求文宣】有啲懷念極醜惡大叔","createTime":"2019-09-23T11:14:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T02:38:17.000Z","uid":70493,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a4962a57a164f61a12db776fcd55f213f97fb3b6","tid":1589650,"uid":70493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:14:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uwxkc4ngNnA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Duwxkc4ngNnA&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK6wAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=4662b532\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uwxkc4ngNnA</a><br />\n以前好鍾意睇極醜惡大叔啲片，<br />\n成日鬧警犬點濫權兼愚蠢，仲可以為大家帶來歡樂。<br />\n但係近年好似少咗見佢出片。<br />\n我地好需要有個頻道不斷咁揭示警犬嘅醜惡。<br />\n人人都可以做大叔，係咪？"},{"pid":"7460484f70b330591a3356c177aaa6511d976766","tid":1589650,"uid":70493,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:15:45.000Z","msg":"「嗱，香港警犬呢，就好撚黑暗醜惡嘅。不過除咗黑暗醜惡之外，仲好撚 on 9 喎！」"},{"pid":"d4938b0da6a0cb83adf59eab20bfe092e6130e04","tid":1589650,"uid":70493,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:16:02.000Z","msg":"「你係咪有特權？！你係咪大撚晒？！」<br />\n「你係咪有特權？！你係咪大撚晒？！」<br />\n「你係咪有特權？！你係咪大撚晒？！」"},{"pid":"e452508f4f98101a19106ad1216d6c9cba0ebb41","tid":1589650,"uid":204728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7460484f70b330591a3356c177aaa6511d976766","tid":1589650,"uid":70493,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:15:45.000Z","msg":"「嗱，香港警犬呢，就好撚黑暗醜惡嘅。不過除咗黑暗醜惡之外，仲好撚 on 9 喎！」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:16:19.000Z","msg":"有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8a2e1beed48acd67dfc5fe1be742aa4046afce5","tid":1589650,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:16:32.000Z","msg":"嘩 紙皮都得"},{"pid":"ccf375f54dece6d946f98183c9f392e6351b9530","tid":1589650,"uid":70493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:16:36